        <p class="heading--32 color--836923 uppercase">NUESTRA HISTORIA</p>
        <p class="heading--32 color--836923 uppercase">DE AMOR</p>
        <span class="space space--20"></span>
        <span class="line line--small"></span>
        <span class="space space--20"></span>
        <div class="text-traslate-es">
          <p class="heading--24 color--000">
            Daniela and I met way back in 2014 during the spring of our freshmen year in high school. We had both signed up for track and field, and we briefly interacted as we ran lap upon lap in the cold Colorado spring. We stayed in touch throughout the years of high school, remaining on friendly terms but never interacting more than occasionally bumping into each other around school. After we both graduated, we went our separate ways. Years passed, and out of the blue, Daniela sent me a note on my 23rd birthday, wishing me well and seeing how I was doing. I was rather flattered that she had remembered my birthday after so many years, and we texted back and forth to catch up a bit. After a brief exchange, the conversation died out and we carried on with our lives. A little over a year later, I saw that she was passing through Florida on her way to Colombia for a girls trip. I was in Florida at the time going to school, so I reached out, remembering the pleasant conversation we had the year prior, to see how she was and how life had been treating her. I am sure she was surprised for the random message, but we instantly hit it off and began to talk continually throughout her trip. By the end of her vacation, we had made plans to see one another, and before I knew it, I was driving from Florida to New Orleans (where she was living at the time) to spend a weekend with her and see if there was something there. One weekend turned into two weekends. Those two weekends concluded with the beginning of our relationship in June of 2022. What followed were years of long distance, phone calls, and planning trips to see one another. Through it all, our relationship has continued to grow and our love for each other has enriched every part of our lives. Marriage was the natural next step, and we both wait with bated breath for the chance to take our vows and commit fully to this relationship.
            In writing this, I am humbled by the impact of such small moments. Moments which, in my eyes, can only be attributed to the loving guidance of God. Our story is one of seemingly innocuous chances which ultimately pushed us towards each other. I am filled with great joy to have found someone as special as she, and we both are ecstatic for our wedding to come. Please join us in celebrating the beginning of our marriage in May 2025 in Cartagena, Colombia!
          </p>
        </div>

